title: A Dream Road Trip to Heaven Ladakh
description:
Ladakh Road Trip 2022

Just like every college group has a dream of making a trip to Goa, me and my friends had a dream of doing a bike trip to Leh Ladakh. Finally, we were able to achieve this dream and capture unforgettable memories. I recorded the whole journey, and here in this video I have shared all the highlight moments from the trip.

The rugged valleys and mountains, winding roads, and vibrant cultural life maintain the exuberance and charm of this region. The iconic Magnetic Hill, the turquoise-coloured Pangong Lake, the confluence of two mystical rivers, ancient and awe-inspiring monasteries, and the highest passes are a few of the marvellous attractions of Leh and Ladakh in general. 
I hope you will be able to experience Ladakh, packed with adventure, hidden gems, and unforgettable experiences like never before. Watch this video till the very end and also share it with your friends with whom you want to go on such a trip.
